      "role": "user",
      "content": "A minor delay in the foundation phase? That sounds a bit vague. I heard from one of the site leads that we're actually looking at a two-week lag because of the equipment failure last week. Are you sure \"minor\" is the right way to put it? I don't want to report a delay to the board if we can avoid it.",
